{
  "stem": "12882.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I am-- it's a handmade number, before the stamps were introduced.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it's sort of an amateur.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It didn't do too good a job.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My brother had a three.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was standing on this side, you know, Fritz and Henry.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And 50 years later, last year, through a publication, a book which he wrote himself, Ernest Michel.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] He mentions in the book that his number is 104995.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was standing right next to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I didn't have the slightest idea about it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I called him in New York.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He is the professional fundraiser for the United Jewish Appeal, very known man, a lovely guy.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we got together and just two days ago, I saw him the last time in New York.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We wasn't very happy about it because sometimes if you meet somebody after so many years you say, oh, I've got-- now I've met him.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Goodbye.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That's not the case between us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I'm sure he will be asked to testify too.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] There we are in Buna.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was a new camp, and it belonged to the jurisdiction of Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And it was actually a factory or a factory was built for IG Farben.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Now, at first, my brother got sick.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Few days after we got there, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] dysentery.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "That's something which killed people in no time whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He was in sad shape, and I left the morning the camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And when I came back in the evening he wasn't there anymore.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Later on, I found out what happens to people like that because I got in the same boat.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And much, much later, I register-- I looked at the books.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Germans have one law [SPEAKING GERMAN], order has to be.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
